id="dsq-comment-message-945" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>The IMF is (&#8216;officially&#8217;, HAR HAR) the third biggest holder in the world of gold after the USA and Germany and unlike the USA and Germany probably, actually, &#8216;has&#8217; the real stuff.</p><p>The IMF is the third biggest holder in the world of gold after the USA and Germany (where did IMF get all that gold? &#8230;﻿ ask NATO?). The IMF was supposed to help struggling countries with the gold but instead the world is going broke while the IMF is getting fantastically wealthy, more powerful and authoritarian and is demanding more world taxes while it&#8217;s own hoards of gold pile up.  YOO HOO!  ANY OF OUR SO CALLED LEADERS/REPRESENTITIVES OUT THERE?</p><p>The IMF and World Bank are UN agencies of now countless agencies, commissions and organizations complicit with the globalist elitists and world bankers in sucking the life out of the world and eliminating individual freedoms. The UN should be included in the gold conversation, don&#8217;t you think?</p><p>10 nations that control the world&#8217;s gold &#8211; MarketWatch<br
